	<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading" >Seamus Heaney</h1>


	<div id="bodyContent" class="mw-body-content">
			<div id="siteSub" class="noprint">Un article de Wikipédia, l&#039;encyclopédie libre.</div>
		<div id="contentSub"></div>
		<div id="contentSub2"></div>
		
		<div id="mw-content-text" lang="fr" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="mw-parser-output"><div id="" class="bandeau-container homonymie plainlinks hatnote" style=""><div class="bandeau-cell bandeau-icone" style="display:table-cell;padding-right:0.5em"><a href="/wiki/Aide:Homonymie" title="Aide:Homonymie"><img alt="Page d’aide sur l’homonymie" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/3e/Disambig_colour.svg/20px-Disambig_colour.svg.png" decoding="async" width="20" height="15" class="noviewer" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/3e/Disambig_colour.svg/30px-Disambig_colour.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/3e/Disambig_colour.svg/40px-Disambig_colour.svg.png 2x" data-file-width="272" data-file-height="200" /></a></div><div class="bandeau-cell" style="display:table-cell;padding-right:0.5em">Pour les articles homonymes, voir <a href="/wiki/Heaney" class="mw-disambig" title="Heaney">Heaney</a>.
</div></div>
<div class="infobox_v3">
<div class="entete icon auteur" style="background-color: #4C6099; color: #FFFFFF;"><style data-mw-deduplicate="TemplateStyles:r155517023">.mw-parser-output .entete.auteur{background-image:url("//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/1/1e/Picto_infobox_auteur.png")}</style>
<div>Seamus Heaney</div>
</div><div class="images"><a href="/wiki/Fichier:Seamus_Heaney_Photograph_Edit.jpg" class="image"><img alt="Description de cette image, également commentée ci-après" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/bb/Seamus_Heaney_Photograph_Edit.jpg/220px-Seamus_Heaney_Photograph_Edit.jpg" decoding="async" width="220" height="310" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/bb/Seamus_Heaney_Photograph_Edit.jpg/330px-Seamus_Heaney_Photograph_Edit.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/bb/Seamus_Heaney_Photograph_Edit.jpg/440px-Seamus_Heaney_Photograph_Edit.jpg 2x" data-file-width="825" data-file-height="1163" /></a> 
