<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="Divers">Divers</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Seamus_Heaney&amp;veaction=edit&amp;section=7" class="mw-editsection-visualeditor" title="Modifier la section : Divers">modifier</a><span class="mw-editsection-divider"> | </span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Seamus_Heaney&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7" title="Modifier la section : Divers">modifier le code</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>
