<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Distinctions">Distinctions</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Seamus_Heaney&amp;veaction=edit&amp;section=9" class="mw-editsection-visualeditor" title="Modifier la section : Distinctions">modifier</a><span class="mw-editsection-divider"> | </span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Seamus_Heaney&amp;action=edit&amp;section=9" title="Modifier la section : Distinctions">modifier le code</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
<p>Seamus Heaney a remporte de nombreux prix, dont le prestigieux <a href="/wiki/Prix_Nobel_de_litt%C3%A9rature" title="Prix Nobel de littérature">Prix Nobel de littérature</a> en 1995.
</p>
<h3><span id="Prix_litt.C3.A9raires"></span><span class="mw-headline" id="Prix_littéraires">Prix littéraires</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Seamus_Heaney&amp;veaction=edit&amp;section=10" class="mw-editsection-visualeditor" title="Modifier la section : Prix littéraires">modifier</a><span class="mw-editsection-divider"> | </span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Seamus_Heaney&amp;action=edit&amp;section=10" title="Modifier la section : Prix littéraires">modifier le code</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>
<div style="column-count:2;column-gap:1em;" class="colonnes">
<ul><li>1966&#160;: <a href="/wiki/Prix_Eric-Gregory" title="Prix Eric-Gregory">Prix Eric-Gregory</a><sup id="cite_ref-9" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-9"><span class="cite_crochet">[</span>9<span class="cite_crochet">]</span></a></sup></li>
<li>1967&#160;: <a href="/wiki/Prix_Cholmondeley" title="Prix Cholmondeley">Prix Cholmondeley</a><sup id="cite_ref-10" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-10"><span class="cite_crochet">[</span>10<span class="cite_crochet">]</span></a></sup></li>
<li>1968&#160;: <a href="/wiki/Prix_Somerset-Maugham" title="Prix Somerset-Maugham">Prix Somerset-Maugham</a> pour <i><a href="/w/index.php?title=Death_of_a_Naturalist&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Death of a Naturalist (page inexistante)">Death of a Naturalist</a>&#160;<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Death_of_a_Naturalist" class="extiw" title="en:Death of a Naturalist"><span class="indicateur-langue" title="Équivalent de l’article «&#160;Death of a Naturalist&#160;» en anglais">(en)</span></a></i></li>
<li>1968&#160;: <a href="/w/index.php?title=Geoffrey_Faber_Memorial_Prize&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Geoffrey Faber Memorial Prize (page inexistante)">Prix commémoratif de Geoffrey Faber</a>&#160;<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Geoffrey_Faber_Memorial_Prize" class="extiw" title="en:Geoffrey Faber Memorial Prize"><span class="indicateur-langue" title="Équivalent de l’article «&#160;Geoffrey Faber Memorial Prize&#160;» en anglais">(en)</span></a><sup id="cite_ref-11" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-11"><span class="cite_crochet">[</span>11<span class="cite_crochet">]</span></a></sup></li>
<li>1973&#160;: <a href="/w/index.php?title=AWB_Vincent_Literary_Award&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="AWB Vincent Literary Award (page inexistante)">AWB Vincent Literary Award</a>&#160;<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/AWB_Vincent_Literary_Award" class="extiw" title="en:AWB Vincent Literary Award"><span class="indicateur-langue" title="Équivalent de l’article «&#160;AWB Vincent Literary Award&#160;» en anglais">(en)</span></a></li>
<li>1975&#160;: <a href="/w/index.php?title=E._M._Forster_Award&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="E. M. Forster Award (page inexistante)">Prix Edward Morgan Forster</a>&#160;<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/E._M._Forster_Award" class="extiw" title="en:E. M. Forster Award"><span class="indicateur-langue" title="Équivalent de l’article «&#160;E. M. Forster Award&#160;» en anglais">(en)</span></a><sup id="cite_ref-Bio_AAAL_12-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-Bio_AAAL-12"><span class="cite_crochet">[</span>12<span class="cite_crochet">]</span></a></sup></li>
<li>1975&#160;: <a href="/wiki/Duff_Cooper_Prize" title="Duff Cooper Prize">Duff Cooper Prize</a><sup id="cite_ref-13" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-13"><span class="cite_crochet">[</span>13<span class="cite_crochet">]</span></a></sup></li>
<li>1976&#160;: <a href="/wiki/Prix_WH_Smith" title="Prix WH Smith">Prix WH Smith</a> pour <a href="/w/index.php?title=North_(poetry_collection)&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="North (poetry collection) (page inexistante)">North</a>&#160;<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/North_(poetry_collection)" class="extiw" title="en:North (poetry collection)"><span class="indicateur-langue" title="Équivalent de l’article «&#160;North (poetry collection)&#160;» en anglais">(en)</span></a></li>
<li>1985&#160;: <a href="/w/index.php?title=PEN_Translation_Prize&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="PEN Translation Prize (page inexistante)">PEN Translation Prize</a>&#160;<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/PEN_Translation_Prize" class="extiw" title="en:PEN Translation Prize"><span class="indicateur-langue" title="Équivalent de l’article «&#160;PEN Translation Prize&#160;» en anglais">(en)</span></a> pour <i><a href="/w/index.php?title=Sweeney_Astray&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Sweeney Astray (page inexistante)">Sweeney Astray</a>&#160;<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sweeney_Astray" class="extiw" title="en:Sweeney Astray"><span class="indicateur-langue" title="Équivalent de l’article «&#160;Sweeney Astray&#160;» en anglais">(en)</span></a></i></li>
<li>1987&#160;: <a href="/wiki/Prix_Costa" title="Prix Costa">Prix Costa</a> dans la catégorie poésie pour <i>The Haw Lantern</i></li>
