t?id=277218">Bibliothèque nationale du Portugal</a></span></li><li><span class="nowrap uid noarchive"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://data.nlg.gr/resource/authority/record75059">Bibliothèque nationale de Grêce</a></span></li><li><span class="nowrap uid noarchive"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.worldcat.org/identities/lccn-n79-099140">WorldCat</a></span></li></ul></div></li>
